```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    title Document Signature Flow - ASOF & Assinafy Integration

    actor User as ASOF User
    participant ASOF as ASOF System
    participant Assinafy as Assinafy API
    participant Signer as External Signer

    User->>ASOF: 1. Initiate signature request
    ASOF->>ASOF: 2. Generate/convert DOCX to PDF
    ASOF->>ASOF: 3. Calculate SHA-256 hash

    ASOF->>Assinafy: 4. Upload document (PDF)
    activate Assinafy
    Assinafy-->>ASOF: document_id
    deactivate Assinafy

    ASOF->>Assinafy: 5. Create/find signers
    activate Assinafy
    Assinafy-->>ASOF: signer_id(s)
    deactivate Assinafy

    ASOF->>ASOF: 6. Wait for metadata_ready

    alt Virtual Method (Internal)
        ASOF->>Assinafy: 7a. Create assignment (virtual)
    else Collect Method (External)
        ASOF->>Assinafy: 7b. Create assignment (collect + entries)
    end

    activate Assinafy
    Assinafy-->>ASOF: assignment_id
    deactivate Assinafy

    Assinafy->>Signer: 8. Send notification (Email/WhatsApp)

    Signer->>Assinafy: 9. Access signature link

    alt Signer approves
        Signer->>Assinafy: 10a. Sign document
        Assinafy->>Assinafy: certificating
    else Signer rejects
        Signer->>Assinafy: 10b. Reject document
        Assinafy->>Assinafy: rejected_by_signer
    end

    Assinafy->>ASOF: 11. Webhook callback (status update)

    alt Document certificated
        ASOF->>Assinafy: 12. Download certificated artifact
        activate Assinafy
        Assinafy-->>ASOF: PDF bundle/certificated
        deactivate Assinafy

        ASOF->>ASOF: 13. Calculate SHA-256 of certificated
        ASOF->>ASOF: 14. Archive document
        ASOF->>ASOF: 15. Update process status
    end
```
